    "description": "畅玩这款由《Drug Dealer Simulator》的开发商推出的第一人称模拟游戏，在铁窗中生存下去。进行交易、贩卖违禁品并收集证据证明自己的清白……又或是直接一逃了之！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/52a100fb50ec5cf3596fbc222f468ccc.poster.avif?t=1765282625\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/52a100fb50ec5cf3596fbc222f468ccc.webm?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/52a100fb50ec5cf3596fbc222f468ccc.mp4?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拉帮结派</h2>监狱法则第一条 — 生存下去。掌握监狱里的权力游戏、同帮派进行交易、发掘有用情报、和守卫谈判并且向所有暗中观察的人证明你的价值。保护自己的安全、瓜分属于你的领地并且爬上权力的顶峰。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/cb17f4b6f519b6089d914b3acc1b9257.poster.avif?t=1765282625\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/cb17f4b6f519b6089d914b3acc1b9257.webm?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/cb17f4b6f519b6089d914b3acc1b9257.mp4?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地下交易</h2>有什么比成为一个可靠的监狱贩子更能获得别人的依赖呢？利用你的关系网获取违禁品、管理存货并出售给其他罪犯。记住：别被抓到了。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/921fc379cba210a3d4eac3886f90c1df.poster.avif?t=1765282625\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/921fc379cba210a3d4eac3886f90c1df.webm?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/921fc379cba210a3d4eac3886f90c1df.mp4?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃出生天</h2>始终有一件事让你夜不能寐 — 你是无辜的！你必须离开这个鬼地方。怎么办？收集证据证明自己的清白。或是制定一个精妙的逃脱计划！决定权掌握在你的手中。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/1dd2eb7d03a50b3cde0ddaa8ea322fa0.poster.avif?t=1765282625\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/1dd2eb7d03a50b3cde0ddaa8ea322fa0.webm?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897030/extras/1dd2eb7d03a50b3cde0ddaa8ea322fa0.mp4?t=1765282625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>管理违禁品，贩卖给其他囚犯<br></li><li>自定义你的牢房<br></li><li>同帮派成员和监狱守卫交易<br></li><li>包含多个不同结局<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
